{"tid":859354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"寧波一男子因狗吠影響睡眠 持刀捅向鄰居致3死1傷","createTime":"2018-10-12T12:33:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T15:16:30.000Z","uid":10487,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"61ead151d61caccebf575333943cd7d84d709a3f","tid":859354,"uid":10487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T12:33:56.000Z","msg":"據浙江省寧波市公安局高新技術開發區分局通報，10月10日18時55分，高新區梅墟街道藍庭花園發生故意殺人案件。經查，犯罪嫌疑人王某某（男，46歲，有固定職業，無犯罪和吸毒前科，事發後尿樣檢測呈陰性，血液中也未檢出酒精成分）因鄰居陳某家養的狗常吠影響其睡眠，多次交涉未果，心存怨恨，雙方均未曾向有關部門反映和報警。10日下午18時40分左右，王某某因狗吠再次上門與陳某家交涉，未果後返回自己家中取刀進入陳某家中（門未關），捅向陳某及其丈夫、女兒、母親四人。處警民警於當晚19時5分將王某某當場抓獲。目前，陳某及其丈夫、女兒經搶救無效死亡，陳某母親尚在醫院接受治療（無生命危險）。目前，檢查機關已提前介入該案。"},{"pid":"a5cc5a08f627c6a1430bc500db6a6debe71a0107","tid":859354,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T12:35:04.000Z","msg":"John Wick：<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d047ef566e017a6665cd45447b50c1e308852f","tid":859354,"uid":10487,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T12:35:21.000Z","msg":"殺得好! 阻人訓覺 抵撚死~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n戇鳩架? 大不了咪搬, 洗唔洗殺人~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea5b0807496f8e6096e6d096c92e57f2ee78d990","tid":859354,"uid":10487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T13:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9fe8dc063d442cc8e04b461ddfec694c4f5f957","tid":859354,"uid":67500,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T13:17:23.000Z","msg":"狗撚抵撚死，落地府再養過啦dllm<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbfa8effe04434575613e0fcbb7c254d222c3edb","tid":859354,"uid":49215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"